brief_summary.textblock:
      The purposes of this study are to:

        -  find out whether participants' cancer returns or gets worse while they are taking
           lenalidomide and Bacille Calmette-Guerrin (BCG);

        -  evaluate the safety and tolerability of the combination of lenalidomide and BCG;

        -  compare the cancer progression of participants taking lenalidomide and BCG versus
           participants taking only BCG
